0.0.4

* Fix a bug where videos stopped being paused at all. (Issue #2)

0.0.3

* Fix glaring omission of updating the .js filename in the manifest.

0.0.2

* Use a less naive way of seeing if a video is currently being played, by looking at video IDs.
* Fix issues with opening up more than one video and them failing to be automatically paused.
* Match URLs where v is not the first query parameter.
